Class DefaultTransformationMenuContext

    TransformationMenuContext
    public class DefaultTransformationMenuContext
extends Object
implements TransformationMenuContext
    A default implementation of TransformationMenuContext. Uses RecursionSafeMenuItemFactory to protect against endless recursion.
